OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776712271
OL,3,CMurder arrest after woman found dead
OL,4,Cin flat
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof after a woman was found dead at a
OL,8,Fblock of flats.
OL,10,FArmed police and emergency services
OL,11,Fwere called to Somerton Court on
OL,12,FBroadmoss Drive in Blackley on Sunday,
OL,13,F10 April.
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed
OL,16,Fthat a man has been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murder following the
OL,18,Fdiscovery. No further detail on the
OL,19,Fvictim or suspect has been released.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
