OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776712271
OL,3,CMurder arrest after woman found dead
OL,4,Cin flat
OL,6,FDetectives and forensic teams remained
OL,7,Fat the scene throughout the night,
OL,8,Fwith a large cordon established around
OL,9,Fthe entrance to the building.
OL,11,FPolice are reassuring the local
OL,12,Fcommunity, stating that they believe
OL,13,Fthe incident to be isolated and that
OL,14,Fthere is no wider risk to the public.
OL,16,FOfficers are expected to remain at the
OL,17,Fscene for several days as forensic
OL,18,Fexaminations continue and the force
OL,19,Fhas urged anyone with information that
OL,20,Fcould assist the investigation to come
OL,21,Fforward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
